<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation de réservation - Eventia</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #1A1A1A;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #1A1A1A;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .logo-dot {
            color: #C5A059;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 50px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #1A1A1A;
        }

        .status-header {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
            color: #047857;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444444;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .event-details {
            border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .event-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #1A1A1A;
        }

        .detail-row {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            color: #888888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            display: block;
        }

        .detail-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1A1A1A;
        }

        .ticket-box {
            background-color: #fcfcfc;
            border: 2px dashed #C5A059;
            padding: 35px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .ticket-label {
            color: #C5A059;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .ticket-number {
            color: #1A1A1A;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        }

        .ticket-instruction {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #C5A059;
            color: #FFFFFF !important;
            padding: 16px 36px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fcfcfc;
            border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #888888;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 40px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">EVENTIA<span class="logo-dot">.</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-header">
                <span class="status-badge">Réservation Confirmée</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="greeting">Félicitations {{firstName}},</h1>

            <p class="info-text">
                Nous avons le plaisir de vous confirmer votre participation à l'événement suivant. Votre place est
                désormais officiellement réservée.
            </p>

            <div class="event-details">
                <div class="event-title">{{eventTitle}}</div>
                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date et Heure</span>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{eventDate}} &middot; {{eventTime}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Lieu de l'événement</span>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{eventLocation}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Montant Réglé</span>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{eventPrice}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ticket-box">
                <div class="ticket-label">Votre Billet d'Accès</div>
                <div class="ticket-number">{{ticketNumber}}</div>
                <div class="ticket-instruction">Veuillez présenter ce numéro à l'entrée.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/my-reservations" class="cta-button">Consulter mes réservations</a>
            </div>

            <p class="info-text" style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-top: 50px;">
                Toute l'équipe d'Eventia se réjouit de vous accueillir. Pour toute modification ou annulation, veuillez
                vous référer à votre espace personnel.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                &copy; 2026 EVENTIA &middot; Excellence et Partage<br>
                Ceci est un message automatique, merci de ne pas y répondre directement.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>